com.clover.remote.client

Interface CloverDeviceConfiguration

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    USBCloverDeviceConfiguration, WebSocketCloverDeviceConfiguration

    public interface CloverDeviceConfiguration
extends java.io.Serializable
    Interface which defines the configuration of the underlying transport for connecting to a Clover device.
